rawContent:
Early Signs of #Depression:
1. I just want to go off social media, there’s nothing there, just posting of pictures.

2. I just want to be by myself, and focus more on me, nothing serious.

3. There’s nothing in this world (becomes a regular statement)

4. What’s funny?
(No matter what’s funny)

More than half of depressed people give-off these signs at the onset of their depression.
Sad thing is, even they don’t know they’re in a 3rd-degree depression. They’d argue they’re fine!

NB: The moment you begin to not understand why you should be happy and show it, O.T Law!🚶🏾‍♂️
